para_trans: Police constables to police in Maharashtra state
With regard to cancellation of additional earned leave encashment exemption of 15 days for these posts of Inspectors.
Government Decision No. Narrow - 0919/3099 Q. No.666 / Poll-5B
Madam Cama Marg, Martyrdom Rajguru Chowk,
Read: - Government Decision No. Narrow - 0919/3099 Q. No.666 / Poll-5B,
Additional 15 days Earned for the posts of Police Constable to Police Inspector in the state of Maharashtra
Government decision to cancel holiday encashment exemption dated 21st February, 2024 issued
has been done. This decision is being revoked by the government.
The decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra's www.maharashtra.gov.in website.
